quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Calamity/scandal/woe to every/each backbiter/spurrer , defamer/blamer"
  104,2,Who gathered/accumulated property/possession/wealth and he counted it repeatedly
  104,3,He thinks/supposes that (E) his property/possession/wealth made him immortal/eternal
  104,4,No but he will be discarded/thrown away (E) in the intense fire/Hell
  104,5,And what made you know/informed you what the intense fire/Hell (is)
  104,6,"God`s fire, the ignited/kindled"
  104,7,Which ascends/rises on (to) the hearts
  104,8,That it truly is on them stationary/residing
  104,9,In extended/spread pillars/posts